A Jonathan Harker's Journal Continued
Tej t-xi nka´yine qa jun pres qine, tzaj jun t-xim nya b´a´n wi´je. Ayine
n-chi b´et t-xe´ ex n-chi ku´tz toj escalera, n-chi jyon ti´j tkyaqil ttzi ja extzen n-chi tka´yin ti´j tkyaqil
ventana n-ku tz´el n-jyone, noqtzun ayetzi´n ch´in amb´il n-ok nq´o´ne n-wi´ye ti´j n-b´inchb´en mya b´a´n
