jun xjal najli toj Londres, b´a´n, at jun t-xilen ti´jx moqa
wamiwe tu´n n-ajb´ena, n-xi´ye najchaq tun n-jyone n-agente, aye t-aq´un il ti´j tu´n t-xi´
noq te n-b´is. Jalin, qo ximen ti´j qa ayen, aye at nim n-b´inchb´ene, wajb´ile tu´n t-xi nsama´ne
