nya b´a´n tten, qu´n n-chi b´inchan señas tuk´e tq´ob´ tze´nku n-chi ttx´jo´n. Ayine
b´a´n n-el tniky´a ti´j. Aju oʼkx in kubʼ nximane qa at jun nwitzikʼe jaku tzʼok te mas
