noq tu´n ky-b´itz n-chi b´et ky-b´et aye t-xaq t-xaq extzen ky-b´aj ky-b´aj ky-q´ob´ ky-chib´jel. A
A Szgany extzen aye eslovacos aye otaq yolin a Conde kyi´j n-chi ul. tuk´e jun
b´ajsb´il n-ka´yine ti´jele extzen ti´j kajon jatumel t-xi´ t-xmilal mya b´a´n, n-el oq ti´j
