aju t-xilen ky-q´ob´ ky-q´ob´ n-chi kub´ q´o´n nimxix, mya b´a´n t-xilen aye kajon, tuk´e ky-
q´i´n twitz tx´otx´. Attoq jun tqʼajqʼajel twiʼ martiy. atzun kajon n-chi b´aj t-xmoxin
kub´l. jalin n-b´i´ne ky-qan ky-q´ob´ n-chi b´et juntl majl toj t-xaq ja, tuk´e nim
txqantl tqan mya b´a´n n-chi ul ky-txlaj.
