B´a´n, n-k´ujlale, a tajlal jun ul t-xe t-wa´n. Xi nq´ama´ne teya ti´j, Dr.
John Seward, aye xjal n-chi xq´uqin kyi´j xjal mya b´a´n ky-xim, tuk´e jun t-xu´k ky-q´ob´ extzen ky-b´a´n
twitz. Nimxix t-xob´il twitz, noqtzun ayetzi´n t-xob´il. Attoq
