mintiʼ in chin keʼyine tiʼjxi, mintiʼ jun oqʼel moqa jun t-xobʼil moqa jun pause, ex in chin oqʼe ik tzeʼn
jun ne´ẍ.
Oh, tiqu´n il ti´j tu´n t-xi b´inchet jun xjal ik tza´n jlu mya b´a´n t-xi tzalaj aj at nim txin
ti´j alkye n-chi k´ulun twitz tx´otx´ n-chi b´et? b´i´n wune qa n-chi b´ant wu´ne qa ayen
tzoqpi'n, noq o'kx mi'n waje tu'n ntene tzoqpi'n. N-k´ujlale, tzaj nim n-xob´e tu´n jlu, extzen n-ximane qa
