West Cliff tib´aj muelle n-xi n-ka´yine t-xe puerto te East Cliff, toj
q´uqb´il qk´u´j moqa xob´ajil, mya b´i´n wune alkye, tu´n tok qka´yin Lucy toj q-q´uqb´il mas qgan.
