mya b´a´n tu´n t-ximana qa tnejel n-chi tzaj t-xmoxin mya noq o´kx xjaw, ax ikx ab´q´i.
"B´a´n, n-xu´jile, ti n-chi b´ant n-ximane? Noq n-chi b´ant n-xi nq´ama´ne te qa ayen
jun xu´j mas tzalaj toj tkyaqil twitz tx´otx´, extzen mya at jun tiy n-xi nq´o´ne te
noq oʼkx weye, nchwinqlale, ex qʼuqbʼil nkʼuʼje, ex qa tukʼil qe jlu xiʼ nkʼujlabʼile ex waqʼune
