"Albemarle Hotel, 31 te xjaw te agosto
"N-k´ujlale Jack,
"Waje tu´n t-b´inchena jun xtalb´il weye. A Lucy yab´, atzun t-xilen qa mya at jun yab´il ti´j,
pero mya b´a´n ke´yin, extzen n-chi tzaj nya b´a´n tkyaqil q´ij. ma txi nqanine te qa at
noq ti´xku, mya n-chin tzalaje tu´n t-xi nqanine te ttxu´, tun t-xi nq´o´ne nya b´a´n ti´j t-xim aye meb´a qya
ti´j tme´jel toj t-xmilal jalin t-xi´ t-kyim. qya Westenra
tzaj tq´ama´n weye qa ma tzaj q´ama´n t-xilen, yab´il te tanmin, maske meb´a
A Lucy mya b´i´n twitz. Q´uqli nk´u´je ti´j qa at jun ti´xti n-chi tzaj t-xob´il wi´je
t-ximb´etz txin. Chʼixmi in chin el txalpaj aj nximane tiʼj. tun t-xi tka´yina
tzaj tq´o´n jun nya b´a´n weye. Xi nq´ama´ne te qa b´a´n tu´n t-xi nqanine teya tun t-xi tka´yina, extzen maske
tzaj tq´ama´n tnejel, b´i´n wune tiqu´n, tij xjal, tzaj tq´o´n amb´il. k-ok te jun
jun aq´untl k´ixk´oj teya, b´i´n wune, ojtxi wamiwe, noqtzun ayetzi´n te t-xilen, extzen mya b´a´n tu´n n-b´inchene
mya b´a´n tu´n t-xi tqanina, moqa tu´n t-xi tb´inchena. Ilti´j tu´n t-xi´ya wa´l toj Hillingham nchi´j,
kab´e or, tun mya tzaj jun nya b´a´n ti´j qya Westenra, extzen t-xe´l wab´j
