"Aye wuk´ile tij xjal,
"Ti´j t-xmilal qya Westenra n-xi nq´ama´ne teya jun rat
qa toj n-ximane mya at jun nya b´a´n ti´j aq´untl moqa jun yab´il n-ok nq´o´ne
b´i´n ti´j. Toj ax amb´il, mya b´a´n n-chi tzalaje tuk´e
t-kayb´ajtz. Junxitlxix twitzju tej tok nkeʼyine te mankbʼil maj.
Ax tok il ti´j tu´n t-ximana qa mya tzaj q´o´n tkyaqil amb´il weye
jun xpich´b´il tze´nku n-chi wajb´ile. A q-amiwb´il n-chi tzaj tqona jun ch´in nya b´a´n
aju nixpe aju ciencia médica moqa aju costumbre jaku bʼant tuʼn tkubʼ tmojbʼaʼn. mas b´a´n tu´n t-xi nq´ama´ne teya
ax tok ti b´aj, n-chi tzaj tqona tun t-xi t-b´incha, toj jun tajlal, a t-xim
b´ajsb´il. Yajxitl kxel nqʼamaʼne aju o bʼant wuʼne ex kxel nqʼamaʼne tuʼn tbʼant wuʼne.
"N-ok nka´yine aye qya Westenra toj jun ky-xew gay. A ttxu´ ate´toq,
extzen toj junjun segundos n-ximane qa n-chi b´inchan tkyaqil titzen b´i´n tu´n
t-sb´u´n ttxu´ ex tu´n mi´n ttzaj b´aj tk´u´j. myia b´i´n wune titzen
n-ximana, qa mya b´i´n, ti tajb´en tu´n t-xi t-xq´uqin tib´.
"O qo wa´ne qjunalxe, extzen tej qkyaqile n-qo aq´unane tun q-tzalaje, o tz´ok q-k´amo´ne,
ik tza´n jun tten chojb´il te q-aq´un, jun axix tok tzalajb´il qxol.
