qa toj amb´il ja´lo aju kostumbr mya n-meltz´aj.
"At jun nya b´a´n n-b´ine, extzen ma b´ant aju mas b´a´n wu´ne. Ma tz´ib´in wune te
aye wuk´ile extzen n-xnaq´tzb´ene, a ajxnaq´tzal Van Helsing, te Amsterdam, aye b´i´n
