tun n-b´inchene noq ti´chaq n-ku b´inchene te.
"A Van Helsing, b´i´n wune, n-chi b´ant tkyaqil wu´ne noq tu´n jun t-xilen, kyja´tzun
noq tiʼxku txʼotxʼ in tzaj, il tiʼj tuʼn t-xi qkʼamoʼn aju tajbʼil. Atzun jun
