ju majt. N-ximane qa b´a´n tu´n t-xi nq´o´ne t-xob´il, kyja´tzun otaq tzul juntl majl toj tkwart tuk´e
jaqet ventan. At t-xu´k t-xu´k t-xu´k twitz t-xaq ventan, extzen
n-chi jaw tchmo´n jun tb´anil twitz awal kye ẍplon. mya jalin n-chi wa´n kye, noq o´kx n-chi kub´ tq´o´n
