te teya.
mas b´a´n, "Oh, tal qya, n-xu´jila, mya tzaj xob´a weye. Noq o´kx n-b´inchene te tb´anil teya,
pero at nim tb´anil teya toj qeju t-xmakal lu. Qʼonka twitza, in che kubʼ nqʼoʼne
