"N-ximane qa a Art t-xilen."
Xi tq´o´n jun telegrama weye.--'Ma b´ant oxe q´ij mya b´i´n wune ti´j Seward,
ex nimxix in chin bʼisune. Mya b´a´n tu´n t-xi´ya. A n-tatey kukx t-xilen tojx t-xilen. tzaj t-sama´n weye
