tz´elx tniky´a ti´j tkyaqil tojxix amb´il, noqtzun ayetzi´n tzul. Ex jaʼlo tiʼtzun teya
ul wuk´ile tun t-xi tqana?" A jlu tzaj ti´n weye juntl majl toj axix tok, extzen ayen n-tene juntl majl.
—Ma chin ule yolil ti'j u'j te kamik. Qa ma qo b'inchan toj tumel
extzen tuk´e tnab´l, b´a´n t-xi b´inchet jun xjelb´itz, extzen aju u´j lu il ti´j tu´n t-xi b´inchet.
N-chin tzalaje qa mya il ti´j tu´n tten jun xjelb´itz qu´n, qu´n qa ma b´ant qu´n, ax tok n-chi kub´ b´yo´n
meb´a Lucy, qa myia juntl ti´x b´ant tu´n. b´i´n wune, extzen b´i´n teya, extzen a juntl q´anel aye
tzaj tqona t-xnaq´tzb´il, qa a qya Westenra at jun yab´il ti´j tanmin, extzen b´a´n qu´n
q´manxa qa kyim tu´n. Qo tnojsa´n aju´ u´j te q´ol tqanil jun rat, extzen ayen n-xi wi´ne
weye te aj tz´ib´il exttzen n-xi´ye te aj b´inchal muqb´il.
"B´a´n, oh wamiwe John! B´a´n t-ximana! Ax tok qya Lucy, qa ma tzaj b´is ti´j
