CARTA MINA HARKER TE LUCY WESTENRA
(Mya tzaj t-jaqo´n tu´n)
17 te septiembre
A n-k´ujla´ne Lucy,
—Ma tzik' jun ab'q'i ttzajlen nb'i'ne tqanil ti'ja, ex ax tok atxix tej tkub' ntz'ib'ine.
b´i´n wune, b´i´n wune, ti´j tkyaqil n-paltile aj t-xi t-xnaq´tza´na tkyaqil n-presupuesto te tqanil.
B´a´n, b´a´n tzaj tqona n-chmile. Tej q-pone toj Exeter at jun
kar n-chi ayone qi´j, extzen toj, maske tzaj jun yab´il ti´j tu´n gota, a Mr. Hawkins.
Xi tiʼn qoʼye tja, jatumel ateʼtoq junjun kwart qeye qkyaqile tbʼanel ex
b´a´n, extzen n-qo wa´ne junx. Tej t-xi´ wa´n, a Hawkins tq´ama,
"'Aye n-k´ujlale, waje tu´n t-xi nk´a´ne ky-q´anb´il ex ky-b´inchb´en, extzen tkyaqil
k´iwlab´il kyeye kykab´il. Ojtzqiʼn qeye kykabʼile wuʼne atxix tej kʼwaʼlqeye, ex at, tukʼil kʼujlabʼil
extzen aju´ t-xilen, n-ka´yina qa ma ch´iy. Ja'lo wajb'ile tu'n tkub' tb'incha'na tjaya tzalu wuk'ile.
Mi jun tal tal ẍne'l ma cyaj nk'o'ne te weye. Kykyaqil ma chi b´aj, extzen toj n-xjelb´itze ma chin kyaj tene
teya tkyaqil. N-chin oq´e, Lucy, tej t-xi ky-q´ob´ Jonathan extzen aye tij xjal.
A q-qale jun ninq´ij nimxix, nimxix tzalajb´il.
"Kyja´tzun tzalu ato´ye, q´o´n toj jun tb´anil ojtxi ja lu, extzen tzajniqe toj kykab´il n-
kwart ex aju ja te b´inchb´en n-ku n-ka´yine aye nimaq olmos te ja te k´ulb´il n-chi tzaj laq´e,
tuk´e ky-q´ob´ ky-q´eq n-chi kub´ ky-q´o´n twitz aye ojtxi ab´j q´ankyaq te
catedral, extzen n-b´i´ne aye rooks twitz n-wi´ye n-chi ẍch´in ex n-chi ẍch´in extzen n-chi ẍch´in
extzen n-chi yolin ex n-chi yolin tkyaqil q´ij, tza´n ky-b´inchb´en aye rooks--exttzen aye xjal. Ayine
at n-aq´unal, mya il ti´j tu´n t-xi nq´ama´ne teya, n-b´inchene junjun tiyjil exttzen n-b´inchene njaye. Jonatán ex
A qtzan Hawkins n-chi aq´unan tkyaqil q´ij, qu´n jalin a Jonathan jun t-xjalil, a qman Hawkins
taj tu´n t-xi tq´ama´n te tkyaqil kyi´j aye xjal n-chi loq´en.
¿Titzen ta´ t-txu´ya? B´a´n tu´n n-xi´ye toj tnam tun n-xi´ye
q´ij moqa kab´e q´ij tun n-ka´yine, n-k´ujlale, noqtzun ayetzi´n na´mx n-xi´ye, tuk´e nim tiyjil n-b´inchb´ene
t-xu´k, extzen a Jonathan taj tu´n tok t-xq´uqin. N-chi tzyet tu´n t-xi tq´o´n junjun
t-chib´jel kyi´j t-xmilal juntl majl, noqtzun ayetzi´n tzaj t-xob´il tu´n nim amb´il tzaj yab´il ti´j. Ex
jalin at maj n-xi tzyet tu´n t-xi´ t-watl toj jun tten mya b´a´n extzen n-chi jaw we´ kykyaqil
n-chi tzaj t-xob´il tzmaxi aj t-xi nq´o´ne amb´il te tu´n tmeltz´aj toj t-xtalb´il. Noqtzun tuʼnj, chjonte te Dios,
aye amb´il lu n-chi ch´iy ky-b´is aj t-xi´ junjun q´ij, extzen n-chi b´et amb´il
najchaq tkyaqil, n-ok qe´ nk´u´je ti´j. Ex jaʼlo ma txi nqʼamaʼne tqanil teya, qʼonxa ambʼil weye tuʼn t-xi nqanine teya.
¿Toj alkye ambʼil kbʼel mojeʼya, ex jatum, ex alkye kbʼantel ikʼsabʼil tuʼna,
ex ti k-xel t-xb´aluna, extzen k-xel t-b´inchena toj jun mejeb´le te tnam moqa te tjunalx? Qamantza weya
tkyaqil ti´j, t-xtalb´il, q´manxa weye tkyaqil ti´j tkyaqil, qu´n myia jun ti´xti´ n-chi
n-chi tzalaja ti´ja aju mya k-okil te weye. A Jonathan n-xi tqanin weye tun t-xi n-sama´ne
'respetuoso deber', pero myia b´i´n wune qa b´a´n t-xilen te t-xu´jil t-xu´jil
te jun empresa nim toklen Hawkins & Harker. Ex ikyxjo, tze'nku nchin tk'u'jla'n, ex te tk'u'j
ayin, extzen n-k´ujla´na tuk´e tkyaqil t-xim ex amb´il te verbo, n-xi n-sama´ne teya noq
aju 'k´ujlalil' te t-xel. B´a´n t-xela, n-k´ujla´n Lucy, extzen t-xtalb´il teya.
"Teya,
"Mina Harker"
