kyxol qe jlu noq weye, extzen mya n-chi tzaj ky-xob´a. Yajxitl kʼelel tnikʼa tiʼj
mas b´a´n weye. A wab´j k-xel b´inchet toj amb´il lu. Toj amb´il ja´lo n-chi u´jine junjun
kye u'j lu, ex k'wel tb'anilxix tu'n tel tniky' ti'j junjun ti'chaq."
