jalin il ti´j tu´n tok nb´i´ne t-xupin tanmiya, ikyxjo tze´n b´ant wu´ne.
"Mya jun xjal il ti´j tu´n tel tniky´ ti´j, mlay tz´el tniky´ ti´j," xi nq´ama´ne tuk´e jun tq´ajq´ajel twi´ ch´in. Xi tq´o´n
t-q´ob´ ti´j n-q´ob´e extzen tzaj tq´ama´n tuk´a nim t-xilen, "Ah, pero il ti´j tu´n t-xi kyb´inchen!"
"¡Il ti´j! ¡Pero tiqu´n?" xi nqanine.
"Tu´n tpaj jun piẍ ti´j nya b´a´n tx´olb´ab´il, jun piẍ ti´j tkyimlen meb´a Lucy ex tkyaqil
