mya otaq tz´ok t-watl.
2 te octubre 10 PM--Aye qonik´an n-chin jtane, extzun myia n-chin witzik´ine. b´a´n tu´n n-watle
b´a´n, qu´n mya n-jaw we´ye tu´n Jonathan n-chi tzaj t-watl, extzun a watl mya
tzaj tq´uqb´a´n nk´u´je, qu´n toj q´ij ja´lin n-chin tzalaje ex mya n-xew. ma chin b´aj tkyaqil q´ij te qlax
n-chi jyon tu´n t-u´jin, moqa n-chi kub´ tan n-chi jtan. Toj tmij q´ij, a qtzan Renfield xi tqanin qa
b´a´n t-xi tka´yin weye. meb´a xjal, nimxix t-xtalb´il, extzen tej t-xi´ye najchaq tzaj ttz´ub´an
n-q´ob´e extzen xi nq´ama´ne te Dios tu´n t-xtalb´il weye. Junjun tten tzaj nim nya b´a´n wi´je. n-chin oq´e
aj n-ximane ti´j. Atzun jun ak´aj mya b´a´n jlu, aju il ti´j tu´n tok n-xq´uqine wib´e.
Kbʼeltoq bʼaj tkʼuʼj Jonathan qa ma tzʼel tnikʼ tiʼj qa in chin oqʼe. Ate ex qe txqantl
ateʼtoq tzmaxi aj tpon ambʼil tuʼn kywaʼn, ex kykyaqil e okx sikt. b´ant wu´ne titzen b´ant wu´ne tun
qʼonxa kyspikʼumal, ex in kubʼ nximane qa aju aqʼuntl bʼant wuʼne bʼaʼn ela toj nwitze, tuʼnju el naj tiʼj nkʼuʼje tzeʼn tten
n-chi sikte. Tej tb´aj wa´n, tzaj ky-sama´n weye tun n-wa´ne, extzen kykyaqil n-xi´ye q´il q´e´n junx.
ikyxjo tze´n n-chi kyq´ama´n, noqtzun ayetzi´n b´i´n wune qa n-chi ky-ajben tu´n t-xi kyq´ama´n te juntl ti´chaq otaq b´ant
b´aj te junjun toj q´ij. n-el nnik´e ti´j t-xim Jonathan qa at
jun ti´x nim toklen tun t-xi q´amet. Mintiʼtoq in chin jtane ik tzeʼn iltoq tiʼj tuʼn nwatle,
kyja´tzun na´mxtaq ky-xi´ye, xi nqanine te doctor Seward tu´n ttzaj tq´o´n jun ch´in opiáceo weye,
ik tza´n mya b´a´n n-watle toj qonik´en tzaj. Tukʼil nim t-xtalbʼil tzaj tqʼoʼn ambʼil weye tuʼn nxiʼye jtal
draught, aju tzaj tqʼoʼn weye, tzaj tqʼamaʼn weye qa mlaytoq bʼant jun nya bʼaʼn wuʼne, ik tzeʼn bʼaj
nimxix t-xilen... ma tz´ok nq´o´ne, extzen n-chin ayone tun n-watle, a t-xilen t-xilen. Ayine
qʼuqli nkʼuʼje qa mintiʼ ma bʼant nya bʼaʼn wuʼne, tuʼnju aj t-xi tzyet tuʼn t-xi t-xoʼn watl wukʼile, jun akʼaj xobʼajil
n-tzaj: tun t-xi´ n-b´inchene jun xjal mya b´a´n tun t-xi´ nq´o´ne wipumale ti´j tipumal
n-jaw we´. B´a´n t-xi nqanine. tzalu n-tzaj watl. Qalte.
CAPÍTULO 20
JONATHAN HARKER'S JOURNAL
1 te xjaw te octubre, te qale.--N-ok nka´yine Thomas Snelling toj tja toj Bethnal
