nchi´j. Mya b´ant tu´n ttzaj tq´ama´n weye jatumel ta´ye aju´ najb´il te aq´untl, noqtzun ayetzi´n tzaj tqona
jun xim mya b´a´n t-xilen qa jun tten "ak´aj ware'us," extzen tuk´e jlu
