a´, aye n-tzi´ye tzqij, extzen n-chi jyone tun t-xi nq´ama´ne teya. N-chi n-witzikine…"
Kubʼ weʼ ex ik tzeʼn in bʼaj desmaya. Xi nqanine te Quincey, "A brandy,
at toj n-xnaq´tzb´ile, jun rat!" Xi´ t-xo´n tib´ exttzen meltz´aj tuk´e jun vas, a jarra te
brandy extzen jun t-xaq a´. N-chi q-q´o´ne ky-tzi´ye tzqij, extzen aye yab´
jun rat naj jaw anq´in.
Noqtzun tuʼnj, iktoq keʼyin qa aju nya bʼaʼn t-ximbʼetz otoq bʼaj kʼixbʼisaʼn, in naqʼunantoq toj
intervalo, qu´n tej t-xi´ t-xnaq´tza´n, tzaj tka´yin wi´je tuk´e jun
