ayiin. Mya jun witzik´, noq jun nya b´a´n t-xilen." Yajxitl, aye t-witz n-chi b´et kyi´j
toj ja. Tej t-xi ky-ka´yin aye kab´e tilb´ilal n-chi kub´ qe tuk´e kypasens ttzi
aju watb´il tzaj t-xo´n, "Qa mya b´i´n wune, b´i´n wune kye."
