aye tx´i´ n-chi ẍch´in ky-tx´otx´e q-jaye, extzun mya jatumel ta´toq!
Tej tyolin, aye t-witz Van Helsing mya n-chi b´aj t-xupin, noqtzun a tq´ob´ n-chi etz extzen
ok tmojb´an tib´ tuk´il weye extzen ok ttzyu´n kyuw. Noqtzun tu´nj, mya tzaj tq´o´n tib´. Xi t-xko´n twi´
ch´in extzen tzaj tq´ama´n, "t-xi´ya," tuk´e jun tq´ajq´ajel twi´ ch´in.
