weye, mya tu'n yol, noq o'kx tu'n nb'inchanteye.
Tzaj t-xmoxin tu´n jun yol te ajxnaq´tzal, "tze´n?"
"Tu´n t-xi kyb´inchen. Ik tza´n n-chi tzaj t-sama´n qe ẍplon aj t-xi´ q´ij
n-chi qoptz´aj. Nimxix kyb´aj ky-chib´jel tuk´e q´ank´uxb´il extzen zafiro kyi´j ky-xik´. extzen nim
