b´a´n, noqtzun tu´nj, oh nimxix b´is, tej t-xi t-xo´n tq´ob´, "n-xi ntziyane teya, n-
wuk´ile, qa ma tzaj tqona Dios tu´n n-tene, k-ok tilil wu´ne tun n-b´inchene. tzmaxi, qa jaku b´ant
