n-watl jalin, t-xob´il extzen t-xtalb´il tze´nku jun tal k´wal. A t-tzi´ t-xu´k extzen
n-chi qoptz´aj twitz tu´n tzalajb´il. chjonte te Dios, atx junjun amb´il ikyjo te.
