nimxix t-xob´il extzen t-tijen extzen t-xmakal, noqtzun ayetzi´n t-xu´k tz´aqlixix tze´nku jun t-xu´k jun xjal n-chi kamb´an.
Axpe ikx toj t-watl, at nim t-xim. Aj t-xi tzyet b´a´n qu´n I
il ti´j tu´n t-xi nq´o´ne amb´il te ojlab´il akux n-b´ete toj kar. Kxel nqʼamaʼne te qa at junjun qʼij qwitz,
